---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Refund Policy | Tools Nestt">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-24 px-6 prose prose-invert">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-black italic text-white uppercase mb-8 tracking-tighter text-center">Refund Policy</h1>
    
    <div class="bg-indigo-500/10 border border-indigo-500/20 p-6 rounded-2xl mb-12">
      <p class="text-indigo-300 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Evaluation Period</p>
      <p class="text-slate-200">Tools Nestt provides a <strong>7-day full access free trial</strong> for all subscription tiers. This allows users to test all features, including deployment and custom domains, before any financial commitment.</p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-white">Refund Eligibility</h2>
    <p>Refunds are processed by Paddle.com according to the following criteria:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Technical failure on our side that prevents hosting for more than 48 hours.</li>
      <li>Accidental renewal if reported within 24 hours of the transaction.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-white">Non-Refundable Items</h2>
    <p>We do not offer refunds for:
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
        <li>Users who forgot to cancel during the 7-day trial.</li>
        <li>Accounts terminated due to a violation of our Terms of Service (e.g., hosting phishing sites).</li>
      </ul>
    </p>

    <p class="mt-12 text-center text-slate-500">Contact: support@toolsnestt.com</p>
  </article>
</Layout>
